⍝ PartitionAxis.tc
⍝ ════════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A nonneg ints; X∊⍳⍴⍴B; implicit ⎕IO
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ≡Z ←→ 1+≡B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      A ← 0 1 1 2 0 2
      X ← 2
      Z ← A⊂[X]B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: B ←→ ⊃[X],/[X]A2⊂[X]B   (A2 has no zeros)
      A2 ← 1 1 2 2 3 3
      B ≡ ⊃[X],/[X]A2⊂[X]B
1
      ⍝ inv: (0≠A)/[X]B ←→ ⊃[X],/[X]A⊂[X]B
      ((0≠A)/[X]B) ≡ ⊃[X],/[X]A⊂[X]B
1
